99*055+p0155+p1255+pv
                    v                                     <
                    >155+g:.255+g:155+p+255+p055+g1-:055+p|
                                                          @

   sisobus — Fibonacci via grid memory (g/p), 81 iterations for Gold tier.
   Identical structure to fib.wnd; only the counter init changes from
   55+ (=10) to 99* (=81), giving 81 fib(n) iterations. Each iteration
   does 3 grid writes + 1 conditional branch, so writes and branches
   both saturate the score formula. IP never visits this row.
